headline: Thermo Fisher Scientific Declares Quarterly Dividend
summary: WALTHAM, Mass., May 21, 2025--Thermo Fisher Scientific Inc. (NYSE: TMO), the world leader in serving science, today announced that its Board of Directors authorized a quarterly cash dividend of $0.43 per common share, payable on July 15, 2025, to shareholders of record as of June 13, 2025.

headline: Harding Loevner Global Equity Q1 2025 Report
